entry.string: INSERT INTO `alumnos_grupos`(`alumno`, `grupo`) VALUES (SELECT dni FROM alumnos WHERE email LIKE CONCAT("%",#[payload], "%")) ,#[flowVars.GrupoAlumnos[0]])
INSERT INTO `alumnos_grupos`(`alumno`, `grupo`) SELECT dni, #[flowVars.GrupoID] FROM alumnos WHERE email LIKE CONCAT("%",#[payload], "%")
INSERT INTO alumnos (nombre, apellidos, dni, email) VALUES (#[payload.nombre], #[payload.apellidos], #[payload.dni], #[payload.email]);
INSERT INTO `alumnos_grupos`(`alumno`, `grupo`) VALUES (SELECT dni FROM alumnos ,'[value-3]')
INSERT INTO `alumnos_grupos`(`alumno`, `grupo`) VALUES (SELECT dni FROM alumnos WHERE email LIKE CONCAT("%",#[payload], "%")) ,#[flowVars.GrupoID])

SELECT ae.nombre as NombreActoEvaluacion, al.dni as Dni, al.apellidos as Apellidos, al.nombre as Nombre, e.nota as Nota, IF(e.a_tiempo=1, "false", "true") as EntregaRetrasada FROM actos_evaluacion ae LEFT JOIN entregas e ON ae.id = e.acto_ev LEFT JOIN grupos gr ON e.grupo = gr.id LEFT JOIN alumnos_grupos ag ON gr.id = ag.grupo JOIN alumnos al ON ag.alumno = al.dni WHERE ae.id = #[payload]

SELECT ae.nombre as NombreActoEvaluacion, al.dni as Dni, al.apellidos as Apellidos, al.nombre as Nombre, e.nota as Nota, IF(e.a_tiempo=1, "false", "true") as EntregaRetrasada FROM actos_evaluacion ae JOIN entregas e ON ae.id = e.acto_ev JOIN grupos gr ON e.grupo = gr.activo JOIN alumnos_grupos ag ON gr.activo = ag.grupo JOIN alumnos al ON ag.alumno = al.dni WHERE ae.id = #[payload]
